Class DeploymentSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.messaging.broadcasters.Multicaster

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Receiver<Transmittable>, Transmitter<Transmittable>, NamedObject, PackagePathed, Broadcaster, Listener, Repeater, Transceiver
    public class DeploymentSet
extends BaseRepeater
    A set of Deployment objects, each being a set of configuration objects. Deployments can be added to the set from a folder with addDeployments(Folder). A switch parser to select a deployment from the command line can be retrieved with SwitchParser.deployment(DeploymentSet).
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    Deployment, ConfigurationSet
